## The Problem with Media Queries

Media queries respond to the viewport, not the component's own context. A card inside a narrow sidebar and the same card in a wide grid need different layouts — but a media query cannot tell them apart.

## Enter Container Queries

```css
.card-wrapper {
  container-type: inline-size;
}

@container (min-width: 400px) {
  .card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
  }
}
```

Now the card responds to its wrapper, not the screen.
